{"type": "article", "id": 6913, "title": "Osmosi 系列大理石和玻璃的完美融合", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-28T07:47:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234105X8OtwP3HIgZcqeGr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t意大利设计师 Emmanuel Babled 推出的这套 Osmosi 系列产品的特点是讲玻璃制品和大理石完美地结合在一起。这些玻璃部分皆由手工制成，经过数控 3D 扫描，大理石被智能切割，使得两方的形状可以完美配合，形成一件独特的艺术作品。Emmanuel Babled 的这组作品将在威尼斯，米兰，法国和迪拜参与展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234103TNbge1OKvRPUZ6tW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234104WBRUFDnwyguXf2xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.88386308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;\"></span>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341041lqdWbC5xgQEIHPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234105GHc1KiD8VBXqIRgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.86674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<em style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\"><br>\r\n</em><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;\"></span>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}